
What is CI/CD? 

    CI  - It used for continuos build, continuos test and immediate feedback to developers. 
    CD  - Continuos Delivery - Deploy to production with Manual Approval.
    CD  - Continuos Deployment - Auto deployment to production and no manual approval process. 

Why Jenkins: 

    Open source.
    Multiple Plugins support.
    Cloudbees used for enterprise option.

    go run main.go &        -   to run the go project. 

Installation: 

    https://www.jenkins.io/doc/book/installing/

    /etc/sysconfig/jenkins -> HTTP_PORT=8081      -   to update the default port. 


